@SmartApiary.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5099

### Insert telemetry
POST {{SmartApiary.Api_HostAddress}}/api/telemetry
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "hiveId": "hive-1",
  "timestamp": "2026-04-28T10:00:00Z",
  "weight": 42.5,
  "temperature": 33.2,
  "humidity": 58.1,
  "batteryLevel": 87.0
}

###

### Get telemetry by hive
GET {{SmartApiary.Api_HostAddress}}/api/telemetry/hive-1
Accept: application/json

###
